Miss Universe Philippines - Southern California | Janet Hammond

Entrepreneur, Actress | 25 years old, 5'8" 

Janet is a multi-faceted individual with a passion for making a positive influence. She was born and raised in San Pedro, Laguna and later on moved to Los Angeles as an immigrant along with her family. Now as an entrepreneur and a CEO in the healthcare industry, she leads with determination and strives for excellence in all aspects of her work. Beyond her professional accomplishments, Janet's talent as an actress adds another layer of creativity to her life. Her dedication and drive in all aspects of her endeavors make her an inspiring and influential presence in various spheres. As she takes on the Miss Universe Philippines stage, she hopes to be the first-ever married woman to win the crown.

Official Photographer: @michaelmaniagophotography
